165
00:14:18,522 --> 00:14:21,638
- Est-ce que c'est... toi ?
- Oh, mon dieu !

166
00:14:21,805 --> 00:14:23,331
Angel, tu es si...

167
00:14:24,425 --> 00:14:25,292
mignon !

168
